overview: The Woodburn Inner City scour-a-thon is on the road again - checkin' out all the places where prospective black cheerleaders hang. There are many and they are sexy, horny, and plenty of fun! Many hopefuls hear the call to glory, but only a few make the final cut. Is this the volume to contain the definitive cheerleader squad? Only you can decide.
title: Inner City Black Cheerleader Search 73
